&lt;p&gt;Are you an experienced mental health nurse or are you soon to be qualified?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Milford House is looking for an enthusiatic registered mental health nurse to join our team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Milford House is a 12 bedded mixed sex assessment ward that is currently in the process of being extended to an 18 bedded ward. We have an exciting opportunity for a staff nurse with a passion for providing high quality care, creative thinking and promoting recovery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Would you like to be part of a dedicated team that provided person centred nursing care that is caring and compassionate?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are an enthusiatic and motivated staff nurse looking for a new challenge or a student looking for your first job post qualifying, then we strongly recommend you apply to become part of a positive, developing and innovative team.&lt;/p&gt;
